	    <div class="boxContent">
			<p>Cookies can be erased or disabled through different tools offered by most browsers, they can even be blocked by means of a previous configuration. Each browser must be configured separately, as each one offers different functionalities and options. If cookies are disabled, it is very possible that afterwards it is not possible to fully benefit from the services offered by the browser (in some cases, it may not work as expected).</p>
